dc_description_s: This data represents municipalities for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2021.[The municipal boundary feature class is a polygon file of all Towns, Villages and Cities within Washburn County. The data was developed using a variety of sources including, but not limited to, PLSS breakdown, surveyor records, road records, and deed descriptions.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
